[package]
name = "icy_browser"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.81.0"
description = "iced browser widgets"
repository = "https://github.com/LegitCamper/rust-browser"

[features]
default = [ "ultralight", "native-tls",]
ultralight = [ "ul-next",]
ultralight-resources = []
native-tls = [ "reqwest/native-tls",]
rustls-tls = [ "reqwest/rustls-tls",]

[dependencies]
clipboard-rs = "0.2.1"
iced_on_focus_widget = "0.1.1"
rand = "0.8.5"
reqwest = "0.12.5"
serde = "1.0.207"
serde_json = "1.0.124"
smol_str = "0.2.2"
strum_macros = "0.26.4"
tempfile = "3.12.0"
url = "2.5.2"

[profile.release]
strip = "debuginfo"
panic = "abort"
incremental = true

[profile.release-lto]
codegen-units = 1
inherits = "release"
opt-level = 3
lto = "fat"

[profile.dev]
incremental = true
opt-level = "s"
lto = "thin"

[dependencies.iced]
version = "0.13"
features = [ "advanced", "image", "tokio", "lazy",]

[dependencies.iced_aw]
version = "0.10"
features = [ "tab_bar", "selection_list",]

[dependencies.iced_fonts]
version = "0.1.1"
features = [ "bootstrap",]

[dependencies.iced_event_wrapper]
git = "https://github.com/LegitCamper/iced_event_wrapper"

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.26.3"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.ul-next]
version = "0.4"
optional = true

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/legitcamper/iced_event_wrapper"]
git = "https://github.com/legitcamper/iced_event_wrapper"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/legitcamper/icy_browser"]
git = "https://github.com/legitcamper/icy_browser"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
